*14. Dep. Pereira   26    4    6   16     44:77    14      [Pereira]
  
*Millonarios and Deportivo Cali both with 44 points played the final 
*matches to decide the champion of 1949:
  
First Leg [Nov 20]
Cali         0-1 Millonarios 
(Goal by Adolfo Pedernera)
  
Second Leg [Dec 4]
Millonarios  3-2 Cali
(Goals by Di Stefano, Pedernera, Aguilera for Millonarios and López and
Gúdice for Cali)
  
Millonarios [Bogotá] champions of Colombia 1949

